# Health Tips Related to Women

Living a healthy lifestyle can help prevent chronic
diseases and long-term illnesses. Feeling good about yourself and taking care of your health are important for your self-esteem and self-image. So taking healthy tips will lead us to have a healthy lifestyle.

Let us have a look at some of the tips related to women health:

## 1)Health tips regarding Menstruation:

A healthy diet , restoring your sleep cycle , regular daily exercise and reducing stress may help improve your quality of life and significantly reduce the severity of PMS symptoms , including reducing moodiness and painful periods.

For avoiding irregular Menstruation cycle we can take healthy tips like practicing yoga , maintaining a healthy weight , doing exercise regularly , getting daily dose of vitamins , eating pineapple.

## 2)Health Tips Regarding PCOD:

Dietary tips for women suffering from PCOD are avoiding the
intake of saturated and hydrogenated fats , eating the dark green and leafy vegetables, avoiding sugar and refined cereals , eating small frequent meats ,having flaxseeds and sesame seeds

<img title="" src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="" data-align="center">

3. ## Health tips regarding Haemoglobin deficiency:

   A person can raise their haemoglobin levels at home by
   increasing iron intake, increasing folate(a type of Vitamin B) intake ,maximizing iron absorption , taking iron supplements.

   <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," title="" alt="" data-align="center">

   ## 4)Health tips regarding Cancer:

   Some of the cancers that most often affect women are breast ,
   colorectal , endometrial , lung , cervical , skin and ovarian cancers.
   Some of the helps that can be taken to prevent cancers are doing regular exercises, having healthy diet , limited consumption of alcohol , reducing the use of tobacco , getting regular medical care.
